description:
PDFMate eBook Converter Professional is a powerful eBook converter as well as eBook DRM removal tool. It can easily convert your eBooks to EPUB, PDF, MOBI and many other output formats. It also supports directly converting to the format that suits to specific devices, such as Kindle, Adobe, Kobo, etc.

Besides, it will preserve all the important meta data of your eBooks after conversion, including Title, Author, Publisher, etc. And you can even edit the meta data for your own convenience.

Support eBooks from specific devices &#x2013; Kindle, Adobe, Kobo, Nook;
Support 24 input formats, such as Kindle, Adobe, PRC, DOCX and etc;
Remove DRM from eBooks;
Convert eBooks to EPUB/PDF/MOBI/TXT;
Save all metadatas after conversion;
Automatically scan the device; Easy-to-use interface;

